5:{s:4:\"data\";s:620:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Beaver Builder themes for your WordPress website? Beaver Builder is a popular page builder that helps you create pages using a simple drag and drop interface. Not all WordPress themes support Beaver Builder. If you intend to use this magnificent page builder, then you&#8217;ll first need to find out [&#8230;]</p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-beaver-builder-themes-compared/\">21 Best Beaver Builder Themes for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:32:\"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/\";a:1:{s:7:\"creator\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:14:\"Editorial Team\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:40:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/\";a:1:{s:7:\"encoded\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:28606:\"<p>Are you looking for the best Beaver Builder themes for your WordPress website? Beaver Builder is a popular page builder that helps you create pages using a simple drag and drop interface. Not all WordPress themes support Beaver Builder. If you intend to use this magnificent page builder, then you&#8217;ll first need to find out which themes are compatible with it.</p>\n<p>In this article, we&#8217;ll share the best Beaver Builder themes for WordPress that you can use to easily build the website of your dreams.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-potenza/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Potenza\" rel=\"nofollow\">1. Potenza</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/cssigniter-potenza/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Potenza\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/potenza.jpg\" alt=\"Potenza\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229412\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/potenza.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/potenza-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/potenza-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Potenza is a popular single page WordPress theme. It fully supports page builders, including <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaver Builder</a>. It allows you to drag and drop your content, widgets, and other elements on the homepage. With Beaver Builder, you can also edit other landing pages in an instant. Potenza has a flexible layout with multiple columns and design features.</p>\n<p>It comes with custom widgets, parallax backgrounds, images, animations, and more. You can use the WordPress customizer to control color balancing and view the live preview of your changes.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">2. Hestia Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/themeisle-hestia-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Hestia Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hestia.jpg\" alt=\"Hestia\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229413\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hestia.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hestia-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/hestia-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Hestia is a multipurpose Beaver Builder theme. It integrates with the page builder to let you design your website on-the-go. It has a 1-minute setup and demo content, so you can easily duplicate their demo site. You can replace the content and images with your own data easily.</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s fully optimized for speed and compatible with the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wordpress-plugins/wp-super-cache/\" title=\"WP Super Cache Review: Is It the Best WordPress Caching Plugin?\">best cache plugins</a>. Hestia supports mega menus, custom background, and RTL (right to left) languages. It&#8217;s translation-ready and can be used to <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/easily-create-multilingual-wordpress-website/\" title=\"How to Easily Create a Multilingual WordPress Website (Step by Step)\">create a multilingual website</a>.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-sydney-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sydney Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\">3. Sydney Pro</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/athemes-sydney-pro/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Sydney Pro\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sydney.jpg\" alt=\"Sydney\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229414\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sydney.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sydney-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/sydney-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Sydney is a powerful business theme that supports Beaver Builder. It&#8217;s highly flexible and provides content blocks to set up your homepage quickly. It comes with a fullscreen slider, header image, sticky navigation menu, and custom logo. Sydney has a drag and drop builder to effortlessly <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-landing-page-plugins/\" title=\"7 Best WordPress Landing Page Plugins That Convert\">create landing pages</a> and other web pages.</p>\n<p>It supports Google Fonts, full color control for layouts, custom layouts, logos, and translations. Unlike other themes, Sydney has a set of social icons that you can add on your site to engage with your visitors.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isi