 The homepage is based on widgets that you can drag and drop to add content and images. Beaver Builder also helps set up your homepage with content widgets, image sections, and more.</p>\n<p>It comes with 13 custom widgets like social icons, contact maps, tasks schedules, etc. Struct divides your content into 5 types including portfolio, team, services, FAQs, and guides. You can customize the theme with unlimited color schemes, fonts, and background styles.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ryan/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ryan\" rel=\"nofollow\">18. Ryan</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/ryan/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Ryan\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ryan.jpg\" alt=\"Ryan\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229428\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ryan.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ryan-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/ryan-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Ryan is a free, multipurpose WordPress theme with Beaver Builder support you can use to quickly <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/how-to-make-a-website-step-by-step/\" title=\"How to Make a Website - Step by Step (with Pictures)\">make your website</a>. The theme options panel has numerous custom settings to change the design and look of your site. It has a full-width <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-slider-plugins-comparison/\" title=\"11 Best WordPress Slider Plugins (Compared)\">image slider</a> on the homepage.</p>\n<p>It allows you to add a custom logo, drag and drop content widgets, and add a background image. Ryan is fully responsive and optimized for SEO.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/radcliffe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Radcliffe\" rel=\"nofollow\">19. Radcliffe</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://wordpress.org/themes/radcliffe/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Radcliffe\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/radcliffee.jpg\" alt=\"Radcliffe\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229429\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/radcliffee.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/radcliffee-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/radcliffee-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Radcliffe is another free WordPress theme. It has a full-width template for the homepage. This theme is compatible with Beaver Builder which makes it easy for you to add content, images, forms, and more on your homepage. The Beaver Builder page builder also helps you create your landing pages quickly.</p>\n<p>Additionally, it has beautiful templates, header images, typography, a custom logo, custom colors, and widget areas. Radcliffe is a translation-ready theme so you can use it to create a website in any language.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://gbeaver.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GBeaver\" rel=\"nofollow\">20. GBeaver</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://gbeaver.com/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"GBeaver\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/gbeaver.jpg\" alt=\"GBeaver\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229430\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/gbeaver.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/gbeaver-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/gbeaver-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>GBeaver is a Beaver Builder compatible theme for WordPress sites. It&#8217;s a <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/studiopress-genesis/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Genesis\" rel=\"nofollow\">Genesis</a> child theme which gives it a solid foundation. It has multiple layouts and built-in sites to set up your website swiftly. It also supports <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/woocommerce/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WooCommerce\" rel=\"nofollow\">WooCommerce</a> to create eCommerce stores.</p>\n<p>It comes with inbuilt widgets, modules, custom logos, sticky menus, off-canvas menus, flexible footer columns with widget areas, and theme options to design your site. It&#8217;s a complete package to create a website with Beaver Builder.</p>\n<h3><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-pagebuilder-framework/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Page Builder Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\">21. Page Builder Framework</a></h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/wp-pagebuilder-framework/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"WP Page Builder Framework\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/pagebuilderframework.jpg\" alt=\"Page Builder Framework\" width=\"775\" height=\"340\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-229410\" srcset=\"https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/pagebuilderframework.jpg 775w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/pagebuilderframework-300x132.jpg 300w, https://www.isitwp.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/02/pagebuilderframework-768x337.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 775px) 100vw, 775px\" /></a></p>\n<p>Like the name, Page Builder Framework is a perfect WordPress theme that supports all page builders, including <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/refer/beaver-builder/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"Beaver Builder\" rel=\"nofollow\">Beaver Builder</a>. It&#8217;s a super lightweight theme with flexible options to design and customize your site. Page Builder Framework comes with paid addons for sticky navigation, Typekit integration, and transparent headers.</p>\n<p>This theme is fully responsive and optimized for search engines. It&#8217;s built with the latest technology to keep it safe and secure from vulnerabilities.</p>\n<p>We hope this article helped you find the best Beaver Builder themes for WordPress. You may also want to check out our expert picks for the <a href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-wordpress-themes-membership-sites/\" title=\"24 Best WordPress Themes for Membership Sites (Compared)\">best WordPress themes for membership sites.</a></p>\n<p>The post <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-beaver-builder-themes-compared/\">21 Best Beaver Builder Themes for WordPress (Compared)</a> appeared first on <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"https://www.isitwp.com\">IsItWP - WordPress Technology Lookup Tool</a>.</p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:64:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-beaver-builder-themes-compared/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}}}i:1;a:6:{s:4:\"data\";s:57:\"\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n				\n		\n		\n		\n		\n		\n\n		\n		\n				\n			\n		\n		\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";s:5:\"child\";a:5:{s:0:\"\";a:7:{s:5:\"title\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:52:\"10 Best Web Design Software You Don‚Äôt Want to Miss\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:4:\"link\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:48:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-web-design-software/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:56:\"https://www.isitwp.com/best-web-design-software/#respond\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";